2026-05-08T00:04:41.0376956Z 22    <!--
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0377577Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0378342Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0379040Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0379937Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0380790Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0381678Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0382542Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0383409Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0384245Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0415185Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-08T00:04:41.0415821Z 33    -->
